** ERR
E-01 ENTER CORRECT YEAR!
E-02 ENTER CORRECT MONTH!
E-03 YEAR AND MONTH ARE INVALID!
E-04 NO DATA!
E-05 ENTER CUSTOMER CODE!
E-06 ENTER RANGE 1, 2, 3 OR 4!
E-07 ENTER TYPE 1 OR 2!
W-08 PRESS F5 TO RUN SALES STATISTICS REPORT...


